Hash chain (hash Ecology) is a decentralized service platform of blockchain aggregation built by the top technology team of HHC laboratory in Silicon Valley of the United States.

It includes shopping malls, defi finance, exchanges, anonymous social networking, entertainment, mining and so on. It is similar to the application store concept of the Internet world, allowing users to choose blockchain applications.

Since the establishment of the Silicon Valley experimental group in 2019, hash chain has prepared enough time to present its best to its global members.

Pioneer of global blockchain aggregation decentralized service platform
